Package: mx-viewer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: x-www-browser
Description: Lightweight web browser for MX Linux
 MX Viewer is a lightweight browser that displays URLs in a clean window.
 It serves as the default help viewer for MX Linux applications and
 can also function as a basic web browser with minimal resource usage.
 Features include:
  * Fast page loading
  * Simple, distraction-free interface
  * Integration with MX Linux desktop environment
